Tested up to: 3.2.1
Stable tag: 1.0

Use shortcode to get magento objects via api. 

== Description ==

Allows wordpress user to get magento product details without leaving wordpress.

== Installation ==

= Activation =
Extract the zip file and just drop the contents in the wp-content/plugins/ directory of your 
WordPress installation and then activate the Plugin from Plugins page. 

== User instructions ==

When creating a post, there will be a new icon appearing on the wysiwyg editor. You should know what to do next.




